                <div class="related-content">
          <a rel="external" href="https://washingtonmonthly.com/magazine/marchaprilmay-2017/stanfords-big-health-care-idea/" class="related-post-title">
            Stanfords Big Health Care Idea          </a>
          <div class="meta">
            <div class='author-info'><span class='by'>by</span> <a href="https://washingtonmonthly.com/people/heather-boerner/" class="author-name">Heather Boerner</a></div>                      </div>
          <div class="related-excerpt">
            How an unconventional team of doctors figured out how to provide high-need university employees <span class="read-more">...</span><span class="btn">read more</span>          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
        <li>
